[SN]TITLE[SN]
2017 Magic Weekend: Wigan face Warrington in Grand Final rematch

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Super League winners Wigan will face Warrington at the 2017 Magic Weekend in a repeat of this year's Grand Final.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The Warriors beat the Wire 12-6 to win their fourth Super League title earlier this month at Old Trafford.
All 12 Super League clubs will play at Newcastle United's St James' Park ground over 20 and 21 May.
Leigh play their first Magic Weekend fixture against 'Million Pound Game' winners Salford, while St Helens face Challenge Cup winners Hull FC.
